That's right. Oh yes, that's right, used - I used to grow - I used to grow - trees trees. I had six - six yards. Well then when I go up to the railway - I had a bit of ground down there see, free. See? Well I used to put that in trees and - greens.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Did all you children have allotments or just you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Only me.
