\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 The scouts or something?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Well - oh no. Weren't no - weren't no scouts here then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Was there anything like it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 
Was - used to go - Sunday school, there used to be Wesley and Congregational and - and - church. You'd go - from school, and every year you know - one year you'd go away by train, to Teignmouth
. See? Next year we'd stop home. And then you'd - all meet up - up in the ground, up by church - school, and march off. March up - to - recreation ground.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Where would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Up - oh that's - that's up this way. Go up here over the hill. A - a 
big field, that's where they played - we used to play rugby and - soccer, and cricket, all played up there in that - field. Belonged to the - Of course there used to be a man called here a cow keeper about here, well he used to - fifty, sixty cows. See? A
n
d - he used to have a lot of sheep. Well he - when the cricket and football and that was finished, he'd rent that, put his sheep up there see. And - then - of course he used to he'd go up and sit down you know, they couldn't - couldn't stop him sitting do
wn. And then - soon as ever rugby and - football started again, all the sheep had to be cleared out. See?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 So the big field served two purposes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Yes, and - us used to go have our tea - us used to have our tea up there - one year, go away - one yea
r, see, Congregation the same. Congregation would - have their tea party up there and - go away.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 This was while you were still at school wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Yes.
