\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 But you'd all live in one bedroom?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Yes.
