Oh make - make - make her own jam. Gooseberry and - plums. Well you get - get - gooseberries cheap see. And you had - only had to buy a bit of brown sugar. And then }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3699631\charrsid13773120 \endash }{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120  st}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3699631\charrsid13773120 i}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 r}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3699631\charrsid13773120  }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 it up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Would you grown gooseberries on your allotment?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Ay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Did you ever grow gooseberries and things like that on your allotment?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Yes. Oh on allotments there was - there was gooseberry trees see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 How about things like pickles or wine?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Oh - no. You never - bothered with pickles. No. wine. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Why no wine, was that because of the church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Oh - we didn't - didn't hear wine. We have cider.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Did you make that or buy it?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Cider. Cider, you could have as much cider as you minded. Oh they - farmer would give you that. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Would you make medicines at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Oh no.
