 paid - he'd get paid, he'd come up town - six o'clock, he'd go in, he'd bide there afore eleven. Get drunk Well - go home - row, and he'd come - down work - Saturday, up 'til one o'clock, perhaps later, then he'd come up the pub again. He'd bide there fo
