something. Well - you - you did get - you was afraid you see. So you'd come to - say to your mother - I had a fight with so and so today, and - he's going to tell his father, his father's going to give me - a dinger when he sees me. Well if he Summons him
 see. But - He may say - now don't you - don't you go - fighting again with my boy mind. And - then of course you'd tell him what had started it. Oh, he'd say, he didn't tell me that then. See?
