\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Oh - oh he was a - the for}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2584255\charrsid13773120 e}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 man's all right. They wouldn't - they wouldn't say nothing - no - no - you know, long as everything was going right. He wouldn't say anything. If he caught - he catch - if catched }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2584255\charrsid13773120 me mind asleep - he'd tell m}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 e. See? He said he wouldn't say - he wouldn't may - perhaps say nothing to you, he'd come to me. And he'd sa}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2584255\charrsid13773120 y - don't - don't let me catch m}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 e }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2584255\charrsid13773120 again. See? Foreman would tell m}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 e in a proper manner. First time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Did this apply when you were spinning as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Ay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Did the same apply when you were spinning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Oh the bugger he - he was spinning, you had to - you got no bloody time to - you had no time to sleep. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Did they treat you fairly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 
The machine - machines be going all the bloody time see. You had no time for - for naught. As far as that - you had to ask somebody to - if you was going lavatory you'd have to ask somebody to - come or help. See?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 So it got a bit better really when you started packing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Ay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 The work got a bit better when you started packing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Oh yes. Was different altogether over there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Why was that do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Ay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Was that because of the work or because you were a bit older do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 
Better all round because it's different work, see. Different work. Well one man used to work - one man - one man used to work - used to work a machine. He'd work - he'd go all day now 
what they call a - a - a glazer, see. That would be putting a piece through and a knife would be going all the time, cutting off all the bale. And he'd put the reel in it, in that piece, see.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Then he'd be finished, see. What they call a real through 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Which did you prefer, the spinning job or the job afterwards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Oh - oh the packing job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 But did you prefer the spinning job to school do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Would you rather have been spinning or at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Oh bugger, I'd sooner be at spinning than school. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 You didn't think you'd like to be at school rather than do this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Did you ever think afterwards that you wish you'd have perhaps liked school more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 You didn't miss a lot?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 No. On
ly thing I wish is - when the day war broke out I come home again. Instead of - going home. Then I should have been exempted. I shouldn't have been in war at all. Yes, when I worked for - when I worked for Berry}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2584255\charrsid13773120 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 s, 'course they send me for - three weeks be
fore they ought to. See? And when I got to Exeter the Sergeant Major said - well, he said, you aren't supposed to be here. He said, you - come before your time. I said, before me time? Yes, he said, you've got three weeks, a month left. He said. They're h
aving a tribunal on you. Oh, I said - never mind, I said. I said, I'll go right on I said. I said, after all the fuss I've had this time I says to him. So I went home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 You worked in this packing job until fourteen until you went into the first world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Is that right?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 The same job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 I worked up - worked there fourteen year. Packing job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 You say it was a Government -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Then they - they tried to cut me wages. See?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 When was this, what year?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Oh - ju
st before 1914 war. They wanted to cut me was - wages. See, I was - I was earning a pound and - me - me mate was earning a pound and - twenty-two pound - twenty-two bob, see. Of course the rest of 'em wasn't earning so much, well they was - they were slee
p
ing instead of doing, see. They were - they could have done more - more work than I do. But buggers used to sit down. Yapping, reading papers. See? Do horse racing, see? Well - 'cos us is earning that - they - they kicked up. See like I told the boss, I w
as eager to earn anything mind ee.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Of course I said - I said, they could earn more, do more I said than I do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 And of course I didn't go - me and the boy didn't go back then. Us didn't start. Well of course - he stopped our money then. And us - u
s had to go - go up to - up to top of Cock Hill. See the Mr about it. And of course he - I said, no, I said, not tonight sir. I said, I'll come tomorrow morning for it. he said, right, he said, you shall have it. So - then he paid us. Well of course - Us 
had a - had to come. And of course he had - he had to bring that up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Did you do the same job when you came back after the first world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 What did you do then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 I didn't - I didn't go back in the mill again. I got so used outdoors 
I stopped out. And I - I was home here - of course I - I said, no, I - bugger.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 So what did you do when you came home?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Well I had a fortnight's holiday. And then I went out to to work under Board of Trade.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 To where?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Briggs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Where's that now?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 
Out in the moors. And used to cut - they used to cut And - go doing - they had a lot of Jap - Jap - Japanese people worked there, working.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 How long did you do that for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Ay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 How long did you do that job for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 I was ou
t there twelve months. Right. And - you had - you have to carry your grub you know. Monday mornings - they gave you 'til dinner time to get out there. See? Start work after dinner. You'd get a full day's pay. See? But if you didn't start - you lost whole 
days' pay see. Then you started Tuesday. Then you'd get - start paying - they'd pay ee from Tuesday up 'ti, - up to Saturday dinnertime.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 What did you do after that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Ay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 What did you do when the job was finished, what job did you do then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 
I - I come back - come back here. 'Cos I had the sack out there. 'Course they kicked up that - wanted more money, and - the secretary in here, Buckfastleigh, called Carroll, he put the - he put in for a pound a week. And of course -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Who was he the secretary of?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Secretary of the union.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Which union would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 General - General Workers. And he - he put in for a pound a week. Well of course the week after - twenty of us had the sack. See? So -

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 They were pretty rotten employers were they?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 
That was that, us had to come home. And - I was - started in That's where the barbers shop is now. Used to be a baker years ago. I was up there. And - chap come along, he said - aren't you working? I said, no. Go in Ashburton directly
, sign up. Oh he said, I've got a job, pick and shovel though. Oh, I said, I don't care a bugger what it is, I said. He said, oh start, he said - dinner time if you've a mind to. Or start now. Oh, I said - bugger, I said, I can start now can't I, I said. 
So I started right away. And I - finished there - I went and got a pick and shovel, went up and started d}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2584255\charrsid13773120 igging. And - I digged - us digg}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 ed from Witchthorn Road - down to the Post Office. 'Cos the pavement - pavement comes out on the Post Office see. Couldn
't go - and then you could put your - electric wire in there see. Well of course us - us got as far as there - the Thursday night. Well Friday - and Saturday - I was home. See? He went up quarry cracking stones.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 'Cos he - he was going grammar school.
 Anyhow they was home on holiday. Well there's Buckfastleigh races the Monday, and Tuesday's races. Well of course I was home Friday and Saturday, and - Monday morning come. Wednesday morning, of course I - went up - He - he come. He - aren't - aren't you
 
going to start? I said, no. He says, what for well, I said, I can stop home two bloody days, I said, I can stop home another. So - I said, you were up quarry, I said, cracking stones. You didn't make no odds about me. I said. And I went races, and I went 
Brent races. Of course I went -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 How long did you do this job for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Ay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 How long did you do this pick and shovel job for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Oh, I - I - four - four days I worked for ee.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 That's all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Yes. Then I went over - went over the gas company.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 How long did you do that for, that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Oh that - right on 'til I could - 'til I had - had this. Yes. Didn't do naught else but pick and shovel work all the time.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Would that be about 1945 or 86?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Ay? Yes. Bugger I -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 You've done that mainly since the first world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 You did spinning in the mill and then you did packing in the mill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 You worked for the gas board after the first world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Would you have preferred any other kind of occupation to what you did during your working life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 You were happy with that were you? Did you serve any apprenticeship or training period?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 No. No. No apprentice. Had to pick it up as I went along.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Did you find it easy to pick up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Were you ever a member of any trade union?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Ay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Were you ever a member of any trade union at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Me - trade union? Oh - I - trade - I was trade union man for - twelve months.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 This was the time you were telling me about?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 
When I - when I worked at Biggs - to work. We had a trades union out there. See I have - everybody come had to join. Well I joined. Well - I didn't say nothing, they asked if I was married or single. All I went to do was to 
- to drive a horse - from the woods down to the saw mills see. Well of course when - when I got out there on the Monday dinner time - gentleman said to me, he said - you've been used to horses haven't you? I said, yes, driving horses I said. I said - he s
a
id - well he said, us has changed over. He says, I want for you, he said, to drive a wagon - fetching bits of wood, he said, from the saw mills - up to - house - the houses see. He said - this chap, he said, can't get that horse to go, he said, it - jibs,
 
he said, he says. So - I said, all right, I said, I'll try him, I said. And I'll see whether I can get him to go. Any rate - I went up this weekend - and I started - and of course over come this chap to me, he said, here, Oh I said, he'll go perhaps I sai
d.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 
I drove up to moor and I - jumped up on the shafts, get up, on he went. When along there beautiful. Horse come - to bit of a hill, going up to the - camp. Well, he stopped. So I picked Then I got up on the shaft, come on, I said, old man, come on 
gee up, get the whip and - oh no, up in the air went. Up. Oh I thought - So I - went up to the - camp, I said to the chap there, I said, here. I said, I've coaxed him and everything. I said, he won't move and I thought I'm going to make him move. I said. 
S
o I - went - cut a long stick. So I step on the shafts and - give him a He was rearing up in the air and I - All at once he off. Bugger - couldn't stop him. Oh he went past all the huts. And I was pulling and dragging on him like that, no damned fear. He 
went right out the moor gate. And then he had to stop because the shafts went between the gate. And so I - got a da}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2584255\charrsid13773120 m}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 
ned job now to - make him go back. Anyway, bugger wouldn't go back. So what I do I un - hitch - unhitch the gate, and - push the gate open. T
hen - he had to go to side. I got that side, turned round, then - in I went. I got on the shafts - I said, come on, gee up, up, down with the stick. Off he went. Didn't stop again - 'til I got - unloaded. And then we - I couldn't stop him. I said. And a g
ood job the gate was shut.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Was this when you were a member of the gas board?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Ay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 When you were working with the gas board was this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Oh no, when I worked for Briggs. Worked at Briggs see.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 When was this, just after the first world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Just after the first world war. Yes. Oh damn it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 What did you think of the unions?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Ay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 What did you think of the unions?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Well - a damned lot of - damned lot of arguers. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Why was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 No good - ay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Why was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 
Well the buggers wouldn't work and they kept on asking for more money. They wouldn't do a fair day's work. God damn me - in - down here - now they've got a - they've got a - a - dig - dig - dig up. Us used to do that ourselves. Dig it up pic
k and shovel. And dig up - dig up more than what they do. Cor I - I used to dig across the road - lay in the pipes, filled in - by eight o'clock, or six o'clock hours a day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Were you a member of a union when you were a packer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Ay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Were you a member of any union when you were a packer in the mill before the first world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Were there any union at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 No union - no union at all then. Down here.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 They all came after the first world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 After - after the f
irst world war. They used to - all join the unions, some was - what do they call 'em, General Workers Union. Then there's all the Textile Union. And -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 They all came after the first world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Ay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 These all came after the first world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 That's right. God damn it we - us used to do more work in the mill - one day than they do to - do down there in a week. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Were you a member of any union when you were working with the gas board people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 No. No. No. Only union I joined was - a General - joined the General Workers union, out Brent.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2584255\charrsid13773120  And when I come - up - us paye}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 
d for more money. Us told the fellow - us wanted half a crown a week more. See? And - that bloody fool went and put in a pound. A week more. And - the Saturday after 
when us find out - twen - twenty of us had the sack. See? We had the sack, twenty of us. That's what you get. I said, us now - us now - us be sacked now putting in a pound a week, and us told ee to put in for half a crown. And us - should have got our hal
f a crown I said if you put in perhaps. It was too much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 You thin it was the union's fault you got the sack?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Ay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 You think it was the union's fault that caused you to get the sack?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Yes. Yes. 'Cos Half a crown. Half a crown a week 'cos weren't to more.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Did you think that employers and workers had the same interests, or do you think they had different interests?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Oh the workers - workers and employers - was more together than what they be now. If you went to your employer and ta
lk - talk - talked - talked in a proper manner, he'd listen to you? See? But now overseers - they got. They'd in with the bosses. That ain't fair.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Were these overseers in your time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Ay?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Were these overseers around when you were in the mill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 
Oh no. See different - different when I - only a foreman you come to your com - foreman and compl - complain. And he'd - he's see it is done.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Did you find when you were in the mill for instance that there was a difference between trained craftsmen and other workers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 
Oh - craftsmen - you know - he knowed his work, see, and you'd have to do what he told ee. See? No - no interfering with his work neither. If he had - you wouldn't - you wouldn't - be allowed to go and pick up his tools and - 
perform doing anything - see? You have to let - then his tool - when he wanted a tool he'd ask you for it and you'd pass it over to him. See? No - clow}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2584255\charrsid13773120 n}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 ing about.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Would there be craftsmen in the mill itself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Oh yes. 'Course there was fitters. Th
ere was - six - six men all - all fitters you know. Of course then there come then - they started taking on apprentices see, after the first world war. They started taking apprentices on see. Well now if you had a son, see, well you could pound a week shi
l
lings a week, see. He'd be learning his trade, see. He'd get his dentures when he finished. They pick - they pick it up now - in fitters. Put buggers down in Plymouth dockyard, I know men down there - they never - well they didn't know a damn hammer - ham
mer was when they went there. Now they'm tradesmen. See? Picked it up
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 So you had to learn your trade a lot better, more in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Yes. Ay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 You had to earn your craftsmanship a lot harder in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Oh damn yes. They made 'em - they made 'em - made 'em do everything. So you - you was a proper - now - they pick it up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Do you think working full time changed your attitude to life in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 YES. Oh - when you're working full time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 You enjoyed the work though didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Yes. Oh I used to - I used to like working.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 When you had a birthday would it be different from any other day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 No. Before - we had your birthday, perhaps there was a little book give to you or something see. And - no - nothing special. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 You did receive some presents may be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Ay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Did you receive any presents at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 
No, perhaps a little book. Picture book or a - a - Comic Cuts or some damned thing like that, that's all. May get a - may get a pencil, you know. Sl
ate pencil. One of they - give you you. But - bugger no - it weren't like it - like it is now. They have little parties now, the children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Nothing like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Had five or six see - five or six come down - to your - tea party. Bread and - cream, b
read and cream and - cake. Bugger you - you wouldn't see that in our days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 You wouldn't have anything special to eat on your birthday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 No guests at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 That's right. Same - us should have the same - have the same day every day. Bread and butter and cake or -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 What about Christmas Day, anything special then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Oh - come - when it come the evening always did. When you got - got - all together and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Would anything special happen on Christmas Day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 No, just your own - you'd have a - what I call a better dinner you know. Perhaps you had a fowl or - see. But -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 You'd have Christmas Day off though wouldn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Ay?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 You'd have Christmas Day off wouldn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Oh yes, you wouldn't go work Christmas Day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Would you get paid for Christmas Day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 No. We - no. Christmas Day come on a working day, you'd always had - you'd always had to have -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 So unless it came on Sunday that would be it, you'd have to lose pay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Yes. Oh - Christmas Day don't come on a Sunday. No, you didn't ge}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2584255\charrsid13773120 
t no money. Never - never paid m}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 e or - for holidays. No. No, I never - I never got paid for any holidays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Would you have anything special to eat on Christmas Day at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Oh yes, would have a - you'd have a - 
fowl And - us going to a farmer in Ashburton - and us you give him a shilling a pound, see. Never mind went up or down, see. Well of course They was a shilling a pound. See? And of course - well - one and a penny, then they went up - one and two. See? Wel
l this went on - couple of year, three year I think this went on like that. Then the old farmer was took bad. Of course and - his son - wouldn't have it, you know, not a shilling a pound. But this - old - old farmer But the son, he soon stopped it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Did you ever have anything like musical instruments in the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Christmas?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Christmas or any time of year, would you play any musical instruments?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Play any - no, no, no. Never had - never had money to buy a damned mouth organ, never - anything else.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 No tin whistles or anything like that?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Was there anybody in the family who'd sing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 So you'd never make music together as a family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 How about games, did you ever play games with your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Oh yes, we 
all get - game of snake and ladders. One of they - I don't know whether it was a penny or tuppence. Then you have some dice you throw out. And you play a game of that, snakes and ladders and - and horse racing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 What's that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Well - the - the card
, you have a horse on, you'd have a horse head see. Then you throw the dice and - you checked up. See. Shift your horse up. 'Course - if - you had some sweets - you'd - make a bet. I bet my horse beat yours see, for a sweet. If your horse won you'd - you'
d have the sweet. See?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Did you ever go outside and play with your mother at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 
Oh used to - used to go up the old lady's called Granny Vasey. 'Course - the publican - that's old Joe Orr, he - there was five of us, five boys, well he'd - he'd fi
ll up a bottle of beer see. And put in his pocket. And - then us'd go up - take Granny Carr up this bottle of beer. And go - the fireplace here, and this here settee come out so - round like that. With a table was here. And old granny was at - in the corn
e
r. Well us used to to sit around here the table, in front of us - give granny her - bottle and a glass, then us - us'd play a game of cards see. And I would - that's where us used to get - go up there night times when it was raining and - that cold. Used 
t
o take old granny her bottle of beer. Of course the landlord's some would - fill it up when his father wasn't about. See, and put it in his pocket, bring it out. Well it - well that would be taken. Put it in your pocket then - take it up to granny, and us
 used to go up there. For - probably half past nine, sometimes ten o'clock we - finish a game, see. Then - go up he'd come eleven o'clock see, he'd turn out down the pub,
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Was this your real granny?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 No. No, granny - called Granny Vasey. Her used t
o - he used to be - working on the roads see, quarrying, work on the roads, cracking stones. Always -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 This was common practice was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Yes. Oh you were - You could go round a farmer and - he'd give you a jug of cider.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Would they charge not at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 No, they wouldn't charge you nothing. Then 'course see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 What about books, would there be any books in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Boxing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Books.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Books? Oh - no - never used to - no reading books.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 No newspapers or magazines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 No. Used to have Comic Cuts and - and - read they.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Did your mother ever read them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 
No, bugger no, her couldn't read or write. Her never went to school at all. None, none of 'em - none of the Oxenham's ever went to school. Barring the youngsters a
s coming on now. The - the youngsters are - that's now the sons and that, they - some of 'em can read and write. In fact one of 'em - one of 'em lives at Burntown now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Could you read and write when you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Oh I - not very much. Bugger I
 never learned very much. No, I was a poor scholar. I wish scores of times I'd have - I'd have learned instead of - buggering about.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 But you did want to go to work rather than stay at school didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Ay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 You did want to go to work rather than stay at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 
Yes. I - I - I'd sooner be at work. But I - when I was in the Army I wished to God I'd have learned. Yes. I was offered a stripe. And - Sergeant Major says - it will be a paid stripe, dome on Bugger I said, they'd only laugh at 
me. I says, if I go round the line and say, what's your name? I said, I should ask them how to spell it. I said, bugger, they'd laugh at me Sergeant Major, I said. I said, I - I said, I'll go on like I be.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Did George or Poll or Lyn ever read in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Oh, they didn't. George - me brother after he - few years, he went - he went in the van playing the big drum.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 He didn't play anything at home though?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Do you remember anything like a funeral in the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Ay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Do you remember anything like a funeral in the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Not before the war?
