No, not til after - not 'til after - after - first world war, when I started work. Well then - when you was on a - belonged now to a club - see, well when it com
e round your turn you'd have to go. See, or pay a shilling, see. Forfeit a shilling. Well of course some couldn't afford to lose a shilling see. And - but when I worked in the Abbey - I could get off when I like. See?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 When was it you worked in the Abbey?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Ay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 When was it you worked in the Abbey?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Oh - let me see - I went up to Brent}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2584255\charrsid13773120 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 s. I come home from Brent}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2584255\charrsid13773120 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 s. Two year. Oh about -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 1923 or so?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Yes, something like that - like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 While you were still working with the gas board though?
