Oh 'til I near went - 'til I was doing this - doing that for - six - six or seven - eight year. Yes. Well I done it - I used to make - make stools and - baskets home. After - 
just for - oh say about - three year before mother - mother - died. She was took - had a stroke, then I couldn't do it see. I had - I had to do - more - most of the work then myself.
