He was a - foreman in the mill, designer. And he was a - cornet player, see, and - could play - play a piano, you know, or a organ. Play any damned thing he could. And he wa
s a - good singer see. Well he was the church - church organist, and - used to train the choir, every Wednesday night they had to be there. 'Course he - he used to get about forty pound I reckon here for it, you see. Twenty or thirty - thirty or forty pou
nd. Well - when he gived up - when he gived up the Postmaster, he took it on. Well they said that - he was paid sixty pound a year for it. Well of course -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 For being a choirmaster?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Yes. Yes, choirmaster.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 That's a lot of money isn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Ay?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 That's a lot of money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Well, it was - lot of money then you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Who paid them, the church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Oh church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Could anybody be the choirmaster or did you have to come from a certain group?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Oh no -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Could a working man become choirmaster?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Oh, had to be a good singer and - could play a piano or - organ.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 So it didn't matter what class you came from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 No. No. And - oh damn ee - the - the church, old - old Parson Tucker - the old parson now, he - gets - well t
hey got - They got to pay him so much a year. Then there's - all our They gets all that money. Then he gets his Buckfast. Out here, Buckfastleigh. And I believe he gets.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 So he did all right by it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 But he got - he - he got a bloody good pension.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Did you ever get paid for being in the choir?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Ay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Would the choirboys ever get paid at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 
No. All they get paid is like this. When they go round - Christmas, they go round singing, you see. And sing hymns. Oh - then they'd - go and 
knock the door, see, they sing - couple - two or three times, then they'd go and knock the door and - show 'em the box, you know, perhaps - somebody put in - half a sovereign, some would put in - four or five shilling. See? Well - when boss, see, he would
 
take that money, cut it up, and put it - put it in the bank perhaps see. Well then - they'd go round and get it next night somewhere else. See, perhaps they'd get another - seven or eight pound, see. They go round like that, 'til they finish all kind of g
e
ntry. And - then that would be put in the bank. The day's outing would be paid for. 'Cos it was four in hand you know, weren't any motor cars. Day's outing. And a dinner and tea, see, would be paid for. And then if there was any money left - over, that wo
uld be shared up amongst them. See, you get -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Did you ever go on these?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Ay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Did you ever go Christmas carol singing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 No, I didn't - never - never had enough to go - go with the boys. See, 'cos the - I didn't - attend the choir - choir practice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 So you had to be a member of the choir?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Oh you had to - you had -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Not anybody could just join in and sing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 No. Only thing that - only thing that was - you could do, like a man - see - the men - the men - they could invite a
 friend, see, if their wives wasn't there with 'em. See? See, the wives would - had the first chance. Well if the wives didn't want to go - well you - you could take another - you could take a mate with you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Did the church or the chapel ever run anything like a temperance club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Temperance?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Were there any temperance clubs in Buckfastleigh?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Oh - when you went church and - well when you got - when they got - when you got brought in, But -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Was it called a temperance club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 So you weren't a member of any temperance league?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 No. No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Were there any other clubs organised by the church or chapel, like a youth club or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 No, not - not that I know of. I never -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Anything like evening classes organised?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 No. No. Evening class - us used - us has got to go to school, you know, go up learning carpentering and that, up school, board school.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Who would organize that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Oh the - Mr Abbot, the head - head teacher. Yes, he - he'd be there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 That was for people who stayed on wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Yes. Right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Could a working man go, an adult man, could he go along to the school and do evening classes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Yes, yes, any - anybody could go. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Would this be in the evening or the daytime?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Oh in the evening. Yes. Say seven o'clock 'til nine.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Did you ever go to anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Oh went up - used to go up - what they call night school you see. Yes, used to go up there - used to go up there have a bit of fun.
 Fun you know is all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 What would you do then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Ay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 What would you do, what would be the fun?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Oh bugger - do anything get somebody in trouble. You know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 How would you manage that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Oh - now - perhaps - perhaps a fellow would g
o out see - well - take their tool and throw 'em - throw 'em somewhere. When he come back he - he couldn't find his tool. Nobody - nobody hadn't touched them. No. Then of course then he'd tell - schoolmaster. Then he'd come and - try to find it. And perha
ps he'd - perhaps he'd find it up in a corner of the school.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 So you went there to play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 
Any - You get these young chaps some of 'em you know, they go and - they won't speak and they're - working like blazes and - well and learning. And of course us ought to know better than inter - interfere with 'em. But - we used to just for -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Was this just after you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 When you were in the home would your mother or anybody else say grace before meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Oh no. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Were you ever taught to say prayers at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Ay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Were you ever taught to say prayers at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Yes. But you forgot - soon forget 'em you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Forget them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Yes, when you went to bed by yourself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Who would teach you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Mo
ther. Mother would - mother - your - your sister or a brother, brother and sister would always tell you to say your - say your prayer. You'd say 'em. See? After 'em. If they - they didn't you knowed you wouldn't. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 These would be family prayers would they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Ay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 These would be family prayers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Yes, we'd all - oh my father in heaven.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 You say your mother taught you to say these?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 No. Bugger her couldn't read nor write, her didn't know - her didn't know a prayer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 What about your sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Sister, her - they - they could, they could read and write.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Did they teach you to say prayers then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Ay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 They were the ones who taught you to say the prayers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Yes, when - when - they'd - sometime make you say the prayer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 But not all the time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 No. No. Sometimes you forget it. Fact - in fact if they wanted to go out they'd - they'd - soon chuck you in bed without -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 So it wasn't a very religious family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 No. Wasn't very many religious people in Buckfastleigh. Not then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Not at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 No. Not as a rule.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 What about the gentry, would they be religious?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Oh they'd be And the shopkeepers, they be - they be - called religious
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 But not the ordinary working man?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Did your mother ever show any interest in politics at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 No. Her didn't
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 She never talked about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 I never know about politics.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 She never even talked about anything like the strike?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Or needing more money and things like that?
