o I - went home, I said - if you want your rations - money to go up, you'll have to take it up yourself. I'm going - I'm coming out that club, and I'm going in the Odd fellows. So I went and see the secretary, and I went and see'd the secretary. See?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 This is after you left school?
