{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1780435\charrsid13773120 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 fellow. Same - same with Buffaloes.
