\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13517188 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Oh yes, bugger yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Was she often ill while you were at school?
