anybody - if - if you was died well they sat up all night with you. They wouldn't - they wouldn't leave ee. You didn't have to go - ask some - pay - pay anybody or nought. No. Bugger they - they'd look after ee when you - old people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4329482 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8796356\charrsid13773120 Was she ever very ill when you were young?
