perhaps all - 'til - couldn't go - couldn't come any further. Then her - then her went - then her wanted me to bring home work to her. Go up mill - go up mill and bring it home for her. Yes, bugger - her - her - her used to like working - but - oh her wan
t
ed me to go up mill and - bring home - work, see - they - they used to let - let 'em do that you know, if you was home, you could do any work, they'd - bring it down to ee. In the big house over there, used to do the - have pieces brought down to 'em see,
 to do. When they'm done they come and fetch home and take home fetch 'em, then they get paid for 'em. What they done.
